1 cup teff
3 cup self-rise bleached flour
1/2 cup mesa
water variable

Mix dry ingredients with water until desired thickness -- pancake thickness. Covered at room temp (65F - 70F degree) let sit for 3 full days until soured. 3 hours before cooking, stir vigorously until mixed. Mix a final time before cooking, and ladel desired amount on a 300F degree non-stick electric ingera skillet -- coverd. After 2-3 minutes. Uncover for a few seconds to let fully dry and remove. Let pan heat covered full between each iteration.
